1.00	UCL_Ear_Institute	UCL Ear Institute	The UCL Ear Institute is an academic department of the Faculty of Brain Sciences of University College London (UCL) located in London, United Kingdom. The Institute is based next to the Royal National Throat Nose and Ear Hospital, the UK's largest ear, nose and throat hospital, on Gray's Inn Road in the Bloomsbury district of Central London.	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/1/14/UCL_Portico_Building.jpg/250px-UCL_Portico_Building.jpg
